    <h2 class="section-title">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>
        Bathala Coin (BTHLA) is a community-driven digital asset inspired by the 
        rich mythology and cultural identity of the Philippines. 
        Named after Bathala, the supreme creator deity, BTHLA represents 
        empowerment, unity, and integrity across decentralized communities.
    </p>

    <h2 class="section-title">2. Mission & Vision</h2>
    <p>
        Our mission is to build a Web3 ecosystem that celebrates Filipino values 
        while delivering real utility for global crypto users. 
        BTHLA aims to bridge cultural storytelling with modern blockchain technology.
    </p>

    <h3>Vision</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Promote transparency and trust within crypto communities</li>
        <li>Introduce culturally infused blockchain projects</li>
        <li>Build a sustainable and engaged community around BTHLA</li>
    </ul>

